author: lundblad
msg: Merge r11137 from trunk to 1.1.x branch.
Fix a bug introduced by the recent security fixes for CAN-2004-0749
that caused a verbose log to hide all metadata for revisions that
do not contain any changed paths.  This bug broke cvs2svn's test
suite.  Thanks to sussman for helping to find the bug quickly!
